{"tid":2036734,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［26.05.2020光明頂］陶傑：由得國歌法過，唔好送頭","createTime":"2020-05-26T15:42:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T09:42:55.000Z","uid":201027,"like":55,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9ad57d68d005568338a7b13eade2f0cec8bfda95","tid":2036734,"uid":201027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:42:59.000Z","msg":"啱啱23:25-23:30光明頂<br />\n十九才子：<span style=\"color: pink;\">唔係維穩，咁咪由得條國歌法過囉，歌之嘛，唔值得為此送頭！</span><br />\n<br />\n本來我都睇唔透，聽完又覺得佢講得無錯喎！歌之嘛，真係由鳩佢算啦屌！建咗國，咪唱返自己國歌囉！反正喺建國前後，我地心目中都係有另一首國歌㗎啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論黎明行動塞鐵，定係圍立法會，結果只會被大圍捕，啲狗一早捉晒路，武力又唔對等，無端端俾佢打一身或被自殺。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港獨立<br />\n唯一出路</span></span>"},{"pid":"e6ed66fb1949a38831ef864a36982a3dcf200061","tid":2036734,"uid":254371,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:49:56.000Z","msg":"鄰國國歌<br />\n冇需理會"},{"pid":"0459fb0d98f5c792d97507cfdc4b41e4c79f17da","tid":2036734,"uid":201027,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e6ed66fb1949a38831ef864a36982a3dcf200061","tid":2036734,"uid":254371,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:49:56.000Z","msg":"鄰國國歌<br />\n冇需理會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:50:18.000Z","msg":"正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15dfdd2feef729bf5a06906674dfde0426b29d3e","tid":2036734,"uid":201504,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"姐係咁，如果我哋有共識聽日大家都唔去，而聽日真係冇咩人去淨係得班狗封路排陣嘅話，一黎唔洗比狗拉（大圍捕），二黎證明到吹雞嘅人好有可能係狗扮手足，而之前有一次遊行正正就係咁，前一日喺呢到吹晒雞之後好少人去"},{"pid":"d2e4bdc6466b3119895eb8bfbcfb5472e898f6ed","tid":2036734,"uid":114360,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"15dfdd2feef729bf5a069